{"tid":1291552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對大陸人解釋反送中既網站","createTime":"2019-07-07T02:49:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T00:50:09.000Z","uid":270111,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c87f0c2a01b2fdc436834a3889a637b4a89bdb36","tid":1291552,"uid":270111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:49:33.000Z","msg":"咁多位巴絲大家好<br />\n<br />\n小弟日前開左個Post，希望可以係7.7遊行派D野比自由行旅客。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1283681/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1283681/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟收到好多熱心回覆，tg group都開埋準備開工之際，就發現已經有大group做緊。因為小弟係反送中之前冇乜點留意連登，亦都冇入過大group，結果就撞車撞到七彩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是我地將design好既leaflet交埋比大group，而除此之外，小弟亦都用WordPress開左個網站，原意係向大陸人講多d民主民生既議題，做到「向中國推銷民主」既效果，但係因為時間所限，只係放左有關反送中既資訊。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zhonggangzixunwang.home.blog/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzhonggangzixunwang.home.blog%2F&d=o%2Fu7L%2BZntrZWbswpyROzR2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=b525836e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zhonggangzixunwang.home.blog/</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有QR Code架<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FBL7UHa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFBL7UHa.png&h=5e87ccb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟唔係文科出生，只係隻普通IT9，星期五請左假，搵左兩個fd子幫手，兩日黎冇乜點訓先趕左d稿出黎。大家如果有任何可以接觸到大陸人既途徑，都希望可以順便介紹下我地個網站（不過人在大陸就要翻牆）。有任何意見亦都可以係下面留言提供，感謝！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb21657ad6c86f1391ce1b233f9dd6ae34861f7a","tid":1291552,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"176f687e772f66de58633